Invocation Name: bay area bike share
des:
Let's roll! 

This skill provides a way to know how many bicycles are available at any Ford Go Bike share station in the Bay Area of Northern California. The Ford Go Bike share program has over 300 stations available across the Bay Area ( https://member.fordgobike.com/map/ )

This skill is not sponsored or endorsed by the the Ford Go Bike share program. All data courtesy available of Ford Go Bike ( https://www.fordgobike.com/system-data )
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
